{"about_the_game":"Wagrrr is a game and broadcast tool for online game streamers and broadcasters. <br />\r\nViewers interact with your stream with fun abilities and wager on your Battle Royale game progress. To win with you when you WIN!<br />\r\n<br />\r\nLet Wagrrr add an extra layer of FUN  and INTERACTIVITY to your online broadcasts!<br />\r\nAllow your viewers to show their reactions to your broadcast and gameplay with live on-screen emotes.<br />\r\nViewers can also send text messages directly to your screen through a message panel that uses the same offensive word filter as Google. <br />\r\nViewers can ask each other yes/no and multiple-choice questions on the screen while you play! Wagrrr gathers answers, tallies and displays results!<br />\r\nHosts(you) can also ask questions in real-time and get graphical responses and results with Wagrrr's easy question control systems!<br />\r\n<br />\r\nWagrrr is also a game!<br />\r\nViewers use in-game economy called &quot;treats&quot; to make fun wagers on your gameplay and win more &quot;treats&quot; when you win!!!<br />\r\nThey can then spend those treats on the actions above. <br />\r\n<br />\r\nWagrrr is HIGHLY customizable. Only show what you want on the screen, where you want it, and for how long you want it. <br />\r\nEasily ban offensive Viewers misusing your message systems.<br />\r\nEasy to setup and install in your favorite broadcasting software such as OBS (Open Broadcast Software). <br />\r\nWagrrr currently supports all popular Battle Royale type games AND support for other game types such as MOBA'S and Sports games planned to be added after official release.","background":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1213250/page_bg_generated_v6b.jpg?t=1630961301","background_raw":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1213250/page.bg.jpg?t=1630961301","capsule_image":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1213250/capsul